{"tid":708632,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"天文台嘅測量儀器飄咗去澳門？","createTime":"2018-06-19T12:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T01:59:49.000Z","uid":178072,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5088238ff776ba46531f0eea9897c5a2e5fae6a","tid":708632,"uid":178072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"今日下午，在澳門粵華中學發現大氣探空儀，經過證實後，確實該探空儀是由香港天文台於6月18日上午8時發放的。澳門與香港一海之隔，但如果在高空風埸較強的情況下，探空氣球能夠飄往離發放點幾百公里外的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n🤔 什麼是探空？<br />\n探空是指利用探空氣球對大氣垂直剖面進行觀測。探空氣球下方會捆上一個探空儀，而隨著探空氣球的上升，探空儀便能夠量測大氣每一層的氣象要素，而這些資料會通過無線電的形式傳回地面，供氣象預報員作天氣分析之用。<br />\n<br />\n🤔 探空儀下墜會造成傷害？<br />\n當探空氣球升至高空後，由於球內及球外壓力差關係，氣球會爆碎，此時，位於探空儀上方的降落傘會使探空儀緩慢降下至地面，因此「中頭獎」的機會其實是很低的。<br />\n<br />\n照片及資料來源：<br />\n粵華中學氣象學社 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ywmetc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fywmetc%2F&d=uQGCxC8pIIPMHKLX8tu5FjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=6f015a57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ywmetc/</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門氣象學會<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MacauMetSoc/posts/193489694637797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMacauMetSoc%2Fposts%2F193489694637797&d=uQGCxC8pIIPMHKLX8tu5FjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=549e74db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MacauMetSoc/posts/193489694637797</a><br />\n<br />\n(2018-06-19 18:14 MST）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/202514_8d7f9d61d0f95f8c3ec6551fed4a88b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F202514_8d7f9d61d0f95f8c3ec6551fed4a88b9.png&h=39227e0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣算唔算非法入境/越界勞工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2364ac4ecd098d42dc684378fe502dc67fad4685","tid":708632,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"全世界都見慣不怪"}